params.addr: Address of pop contract to add.

computeRewardBalanceOfDelegator(bytes32,.details: Computes the reward balance in ETH of a specific member of a pool.

computeRewardBalanceOfOperator(bytes32).details: Computes the reward balance in ETH of the operator of a pool.

createStakingPool(address).details: Create a new staking pool. The sender will be the staking pal of this pool. Note that a staking pal must be payable.

params.rigoblockPoolAddress: Adds rigoblock pool to the created staking pool for convenience if non-null.

returns.poolId: The unique pool id generated for this pool.

creditPopReward(address,uint256).details: Credits the value of a pool's pop reward.      Only a known RigoBlock pop can call this method. See      (MixinPopManager).

params.poolAccount: The address of the rigoblock pool account.

decreaseStakingPoolOperatorShare(bytes32.details: Decreases the operator share for the given pool (i.e. increases pool rewards for members).

params.newOperatorShare: The newly decreased percentage of any rewards owned by the operator.

endEpoch().details: Begins a new epoch, preparing the prior one for finalization.      Throws if not enough time has passed between epochs or if the      previous epoch was not fully finalized.

returns._0: numPoolsToFinalize The number of unfinalized pools.

finalizePool(bytes32).details: Instantly finalizes a single pool that earned rewards in the previous      epoch, crediting it rewards for members and withdrawing operator's      rewards as WETH. This can be called by internal functions that need      to finalize a pool immediately. Does nothing if the pool is already      finalized or did not earn rewards in the previous epoch.

getCurrentEpochEarliestEndTimeInSeconds(.details: Returns the earliest end time in seconds of this epoch.      The next epoch can begin once this time is reached.      Epoch period = [startTimeInSeconds..endTimeInSeconds)

getDragoRegistry().details: An overridable way to access the deployed dragoRegistry.      Must be view to allow overrides to access state.

getGlobalStakeByStatus(uint8).details: Gets global stake for a given status.

getGrgContract().details: An overridable way to access the deployed GRG contract.      Must be view to allow overrides to access state.

getGrgVault().details: An overridable way to access the deployed grgVault.      Must be view to allow overrides to access state.

getMaxEpochReward(uint256).details: Returns the total maximum epoch reward given a stake.

getOwnerStakeByStatus(address,uint8).details: Gets an owner's stake balances by status.

returns.balance: Owner's stake balances for given status.

returns._cobbDouglasAlphaDenominator: Denominator for cobb douglas alpha factor.
returns._cobbDouglasAlphaNumerator: Numerator for cobb douglas alpha factor.
returns._minimumPoolStake: Minimum amount of stake required in a pool to collect rewards.
returns._rewardDelegatedStakeWeight: How much delegated stake is weighted vs operator stake, in ppm.

getStakeDelegatedToPoolByOwner(address,b.details: Returns the stake delegated to a specific staking pool, by a given staker.

returns.balance: Stake delegated to pool by staker.

getStakingPoolStatsThisEpoch(bytes32).details: Get stats on a staking pool in this epoch.

getTotalStake(address).details: Returns the total stake for a given staker.

getTotalStakeDelegatedToPool(bytes32).details: Returns the total stake delegated to a specific staking pool,      across all members.

init().details: Initialize storage owned by this contract.      This function should not be called directly.      The StakingProxy contract will call it in `attachStakingContract()`.

joinStakingPoolAsRbPoolAccount(bytes32,a.details: Allows caller to join a staking pool as a rigoblock pool account.

params.rigoblockPoolAccount: Address of subaccount to be added to staking pool.

moveStake((uint8,bytes32),(uint8,bytes32.details: Moves stake between statuses: 'undelegated' or 'delegated'.      Delegated stake can also be moved between pools.      This change comes into effect next epoch.

params.from: Status to move stake out of.

params.index: Index of target in authorities array.

params.addr: Address of proof_of_performance contract to remove.

setParams(uint256,uint32,uint256,uint32,.details: Set all configurable parameters at once.

params._cobbDouglasAlphaDenominator: Denominator for cobb douglas alpha factor.
params._cobbDouglasAlphaNumerator: Numerator for cobb douglas alpha factor.
params._minimumPoolStake: Minimum amount of stake required in a pool to collect rewards.
params._rewardDelegatedStakeWeight: How much delegated stake is weighted vs operator stake, in ppm.

setStakingPalAddress(bytes32,address).details: Allows the operator to update the staking pal address.

params.newStakingPalAddress: Address of the new staking pal.

stake(uint256).details: Stake GRG tokens. Tokens are deposited into the GRG Vault.      Unstake to retrieve the GRG. Stake is in the 'Active' status.

transferOwnership(address).details: Change the owner of this contract.

unstake(uint256).details: Unstake. Tokens are withdrawn from the GRG Vault and returned to      the staker. Stake must be in the 'undelegated' status in both the      current and next epoch in order to be unstaked.

withdrawDelegatorRewards(bytes32).details: Withdraws the caller's WETH rewards that have accumulated      until the last epoch.
